          .img_wrap(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-50px);opacity:0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity:1")
            img(
              src="https://cdn.thegentlemansjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/freestyle-6601-900x600-c-center.jpg",
              alt=""
            )
          h3(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-50px);opacity:0" data-bottom="transform: translateY(0px);opacity:1") Step2. 划水加速
          p(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-50px);opacity:0" data-bottom="transform: translateY(0px);opacity:1") 當浪距離你一個衝浪板的距離時，將頭縮回看向正前方，並開始划水加速
