          .img_wrap(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-50px);opacity:0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity:1")
            img(
              src="https://www.getreadyhk.com/images/stories/lifestyle/big-wave-bay/tai_long_wan_05.jpg",
              alt=""
            )
          h3(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-50px);opacity:0" data-bottom="transform: translateY(0px);opacity:1") Step3. 瞬間波比跳
          p(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-50px);opacity:0" data-bottom="transform: translateY(0px);opacity:1") 當你覺得浪開始載著你和衝浪板時，抓準時機，用手撐起來，腳同時跳起成蹲姿，像是跳到一半的波比跳

